      "comment": "LEGEND BLUE BUZZ (1) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at Gawler over 400m behind Speed Raider (24.21) in a Maiden. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. REGAL MACK (7) comes off a moderate effort last start, finishing fourth at this track over 342m behind Baluarte (20.45). Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Better than last start and can bounce back. REGAL REBA (8) has placed only once and remains a maiden after seven runs. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expected to feature in the finish. CRUSTY DUSTY (2) has definite claims at his first try at this circuit.",
